e":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0e8e3435bff606e695898d14a3922775a6831cd8","tid":1113051,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:11:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Assembly 唔係快d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>你咪用assemby 囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>ASIC呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>解決個client最快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我上面就係想講ASIC 點解係咁負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T05:21:35.000Z","msg":"application specific integrated circuit唔係programming language<br />\n<br />\nASIC programming language慢"},{"pid":"05c4e12dfc95bf0d2e6a79f13d205ae402e0a129","tid":1113051,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"643efe9caeae7d5636085feeb8bf7dd3a3edc1c0","tid":1113051,"uid":22362,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"因為接近hardware<br />\nhigh level language係要一層一層complie成machine instruction最後先會execute"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁其實有無其他 language 會 compile 成 machine instruction?<br />\n如果我無記錯好似 windows/Linux/unix 本身都係 C，所以用 C 寫 application program 係 native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry 主要寫 java/nodejs/sql/php 唔係好熟 os level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"87405864f880f611d784fd0c4d3b95ee252568ff","tid":1113051,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05c4e12dfc95bf0d2e6a79f13d205ae402e0a129","tid":1113051,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"643efe9caeae7d5636085feeb8bf7dd3a3edc1c0","tid":1113051,"uid":22362,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"因為接近hardware<br />\nhigh level language係要一層一層complie成machine instruction最後先會execute"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁其實有無其他 language 會 compile 成 machine instruction?<br />\n如果我無記錯好似 windows/Linux/unix 本身都係 C，所以用 C 寫 application program 係 native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nSorry 主要寫 java/nodejs/sql/php 唔係好熟 os level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:51:41.000Z","msg":"雖然想講大把 但係諗諗下好多流行lang都唔係compile做machine code<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有就一定有"},{"pid":"e73bfd772ed8cb9c6d49299cf533581d97e3d133","tid":1113051,"uid":191231,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"39aed81b22a2f61c6d9782c0bf94c9a2a0b32549","tid":1113051,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T04:53:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>因為接近hardware<br />\nhigh level language係要一層一層complie成machine instruction最後先會execute</blockquote><br />\n如果改IC design 去做某種operation 係咪更快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人話用high level programming languages時 可以修改底層嘅C令佢更快 其實點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:02:04.000Z","msg":"首先 interpreted language 因為唔係直接save左做machine code，execution 時要變返做executable (JIT) / 用interpretor 係會有time overhead；但相對上interpreted language 有彈性，例如generic / weak type 等等既語法，由於唔知實際上係咩type、variable佔幾多byte，memory allocation 真係run time 先determine 到，所以無可能用machine code去寫，最多係預先判斷幾個可能既machine code 版本，execute 時再揀返岩既拼埋(即係JIT)，但以上揀同拼再快都要花時間，即係time overhead。<br />\n(有傳PHP 未做到JIT係同generic type 有關)<br />\n不過就算compile 左做machine code其實快同慢係有好多因素<br />\n主要都係睇compiler optimization 做得好唔好，又或者你寫既code 同compiler optimization 夾唔夾。ED都係深野，讀master / 大公司做既人先識喇。<br />\n直接寫assembly 個前題係要你自己既optimization skills 叻過compiler 既benchmark optimization (係有可能，因為compiler 既optimization goal係for general case optimized)。<br />\n另外有時係睇你個program 係做乜。<br />\n舉個例子，CPU 係 general purpose integrated circuit ，GPU 就係asic；CPU行到既machine code 唔可以係GPU上直接run，因為個instruction set差太遠。GPU要用opengl、opencl、Apple metal 之類既language 先compile到做executable；GPU係single instruction multiple data，CPU就係single instruction single data (真係TERM呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ；大體呢講GPU行Float-point operation 係快過CPU，但只可以行parallelizable algorithm。"},{"pid":"8e1ddc89ce8e732662d26b6c7e4601bd80eac4fb","tid":1113051,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"唔用算盤0既咩做PROGRAMMER"},{"pid":"a745c280f7c477710f27537ecc12745997a0bc35","tid":1113051,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8e1ddc89ce8e732662d26b6c7e4601bd80eac4fb","tid":1113051,"uid":196625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T08:46:14.000Z","msg":"唔用算盤0既咩做PROGRAMMER"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:29:38.000Z","msg":"用開小算盤"},{"pid":"428dcd3550b0a87e066a7c835447561fd4dca9b5","tid":1113051,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T09:46:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>因為接近hardware<br />\nhigh level language係要一層一層complie成machine instruction最後先會execute</blockquote><br />\n如果改IC design 去做某種operation 係咪更快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲人話用high level programming languages時 可以修改底層嘅C令佢更快 其實點做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>首先 interpreted language 因為唔係直接save左做machine code，execution 時要變返做executable (JIT) / 用interpretor 係會有time overhead；但相對上interpreted language 有彈性，例如generic / weak type 等等既語法，由於唔知實際上係咩type、variable佔幾多byte，memory allocation 真係run time 先determine 到，所以無可能用machine code去寫，最多係預先判斷幾個可能既machine code 版本，execute 時再揀返岩既拼埋(即係JIT)，但以上揀同拼再快都要花時間，即係time overhead。<br />\n(有傳PHP 未做到JIT係同generic type 有關)<br />\n不過就算compile 左做machine code其實快同慢係有好多因素<br />\n主要都係睇compiler optimization 做得好唔好，又或者你寫既code 同compiler optimization 夾唔夾。ED都係深野，讀master / 大公司做既人先識喇。<br />\n直接寫assembly 個前題係要你自己既optimization skills 叻過compiler 既benchmark optimization (係有可能，因為compiler 既optimization goal係for general case optimized)。<br />\n另外有時係睇你個program 係做乜。<br />\n舉個例子，CPU 係 general purpose integrated circuit ，GPU 就係asic；CPU行到既machine code 唔可以係GPU上直接run，因為個instruction set差太遠。GPU要用opengl、opencl、Apple metal 之類既language 先compile到做executable；GPU係single instruction multiple data，CPU就係single instruction single data (真係TERM呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) ；大體呢講GPU行Float-point operation 係快過CPU，但只可以行parallelizable algorithm。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />學到野"},{"pid":"7361c6da7ada2ebc4402f2df7c8b5e2d84009e92","tid":1113051,"uid":129573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"87405864f880f611d784fd0c4d3b95ee252568ff","tid":1113051,"uid":147721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05c4e12dfc95bf0d2e6a79f13d205ae402e0a129","tid":1113051,"uid":66242,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"643efe9caeae7d5636085feeb8bf7dd3a3edc1c0","tid":1113051,"uid":22362,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-04-17T18:14:12.000Z","msg":"因為接近hardware<br />\nhigh level language係要一層一層complie成machine instruction最後先會execute"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-19T06:24:15.000Z","msg":"咁其實有無其他 language 會 compile 成 machine instruction?<br />\n如果我無記錯好似 windows/Linux/unix 本身都係 C，所以用 C 寫 application program 係 native <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" cl